{"id":389777,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ed_Harris","text":"Edward Allen \"Ed\" Harris (born November 28, 1950) is an American actor, writer, and director. He is best known for his roles in \"Pollock\", \"Appaloosa\", \"The Rock\", \"The Abyss\", \"A Beautiful Mind\", \"A History of Violence\", \"Enemy at the Gates\", \"The Right Stuff\", \"Gone Baby Gone\", and \"Paris Trout\". He won an Golden Globe Award, an Drama Desk Award, and an Screen Actors Guild Award.\nHarris was born on November 28, 1950 in Inglewood, New Jersey. He was raised in Tenafly, New Jersey. Harris studied at Tenafly High School and at Columbia University. He married Amy Madigan in 1983. They have one daughter, Lily Dolores, born in 1993. Harris now lives in Los Angeles, California. His father was actor Bob L. Harris.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Americans","surface_form":"American","offset":56},{"uri":"Pollock_(movie)","surface_form":"Pollock","offset":129},{"uri":"Appaloosa","surface_form":"Appaloosa","offset":140},{"uri":"The_Rock_(movie)","surface_form":"The Rock","offset":153},{"uri":"The_Abyss","surface_form":"The Abyss","offset":165},{"uri":"A_Beautiful_Mind","surface_form":"A Beautiful Mind","offset":178},{"uri":"A_History_of_Violence","surface_form":"A History of Violence","offset":198},{"uri":"Enemy_at_the_Gates","surface_form":"Enemy at the Gates","offset":223},{"uri":"The_Right_Stuff","surface_form":"The Right Stuff","offset":245},{"uri":"Gone_Baby_Gone","surface_form":"Gone Baby Gone","offset":264},{"uri":"Paris_Trout","surface_form":"Paris Trout","offset":286},{"uri":"Golden_Globe_Award","surface_form":"Golden Globe Award","offset":310},{"uri":"Drama_Desk_Award","surface_form":"Drama Desk Award","offset":333},{"uri":"Screen_Actors_Guild_Award","surface_form":"Screen Actors Guild Award","offset":358},{"uri":"Inglewood%2C_New_Jersey","surface_form":"Inglewood","offset":425},{"uri":"New_Jersey","surface_form":"New Jersey","offset":436},{"uri":"Tenafly%2C_New_Jersey","surface_form":"Tenafly","offset":465},{"uri":"Tenafly_High_School","surface_form":"Tenafly High School","offset":504},{"uri":"Columbia_University","surface_form":"Columbia University","offset":531},{"uri":"Los_Angeles%2C_California","surface_form":"Los Angeles","offset":656},{"uri":"California","surface_form":"California","offset":669},{"uri":"Bob_L._Harris","surface_form":"Bob L. Harris","offset":702}]}